Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caught you, St. Tail!\NYou won't get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were the thief, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You had me fooled all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I wasn't fooling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time I just couldn't\Nget myself to tell you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, I just can't get myself\Nto tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I'm St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely can't tell him. And I\Ndefinitely can't let him catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A FAKE CALLING CARD!?\NTHE SECRET OF THE PERFUME TRAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Addressed to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it my imagination? Aren't the girls\Nputting extra effort into their hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. And here's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A cosmetic company is looking for\Na girl to introduce their new shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari says that he's taking\Na photo to compete in the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These hands will be sending\Na supermodel into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing different.\NJust doing his same old stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Meimi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you fight it?\NShe's got beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail's hair is\Na hundred times prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't change either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil!\NIt's a notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What will it be this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me have a look!\N-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow night I will be stealing\Nthe Parfum Takarada Special. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's going after some perfume?\N-So that's the next caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this supposed to mean? I didn 't\Nsend this notice. Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such deep prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You look very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just lost my father\Nin an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a perfumer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He developed fragrances\Nfor perfumes, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Before his death, he mentioned\Na new perfume that was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was very happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfume? Could it be--?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But just before it was to be completed,\Nhe got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When Father died, he had\Na notebook clenched in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook contained the formula\Nfor his new perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father passionately loved\Nhis work until the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the final ingredient\Nwasn't written in the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that he's gone,\Nwe don't have any idea what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. You don't have a single clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The last entry in the notebook\Nwas "Earring of Snow."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was written like a secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a flower\Nthat blossoms in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you in deep prayer trying\Nto find out what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I will definitely complete\NFather's perfume on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what is troubling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for God's help,\Nfor the sake of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After Father's death, my brother\Nhas become a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't care about the perfume,\Nonly about how much he can sell it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He is planning an outrageous scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we raise flowers and\Nconcoct ingredients for the perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the Parfum\NTakarada Special, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't mass-produced it yet,\Nso this is the only bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For St. Tail to crave this,\Nshe must see its true value.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave the security to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the security a big thing,\Nas extravagant as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As extravagant as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm selling this to a major\Nmanufacturer in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a disaster\Nif it gets stolen before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's a product\Nthat's sure to be a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a smash hit with the help\Nof our little St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A St. Tail brand perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That fake notice was probably sent by\NMiss Takarada's brother to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He is trying to sell an incomplete\Nperfume formula for a high price...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...by advertising it as "a perfume\Nworth being stolen by St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His sister, Yuriko,\Nsays that she's against...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...sending the incomplete formula\Nout on the market...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and deceiving people\Nwith false advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, you'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Let's make the best\Nof that fake calling card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now, let's begin\Nour long homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the petals are falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-The cherry blossoms in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the flowers hold\Nuntil school is out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness. Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have you go out to play in\Nthe yard for this hour of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for this hour now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, they're supposed\Nto be junior high students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the season\Nor do they just want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari, how could you bring\Nyour camera at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You amateur, it's in\Nbeautiful scenery like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...when true beauty\Ncan be photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the difference?\NMeimi looks the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Meimi, come, come!\N-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?\NThat's totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want\Nto ask you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the secret code\N"Earring of Snow" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. knows a lot of things.\NHe just might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So winter flowers,\Nwhat kind are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just one I've heard of.\NWhen I was 5 years old, my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a story that\Ngoes back to the Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a story that\Ngoes way back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in nature\Nhas a color, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the sky is blue\Nand the clouds are gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the snow went to see God...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...and told him, "It's unfair\Nthat I have no color."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God told the snow, "Ask a flower\Nto give you its color."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't a single flower that\Nwould give the cold snow its color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just as the snow was\Nabout to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...a flower came forth and said,\N"You can have my white color."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, it's said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...the snow protects that small flower\Nduring the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got to be it!\NWhat's the name of that flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was\Na delicious-sounding name but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! You're hopeless\Nat the crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all worked up over?\NIt's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know about the flower\Nthat is able to survive near snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell him I'm St. Tail.\NI definitely can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.\NMeimi, come over here a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mother. Mother.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. It's not my birthday or our\Nwedding anniversary, but a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, just open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You two are terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my new magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you! Just look at this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Snow? Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, it's a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...but isn't it\Na bit off-season for snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What am I going to do?\NThe dinner has...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi seemed depressed.\NI was trying to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. She was moaning\Nin her sleep last night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something\Nhappened at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NShe's our daughter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get herself back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, well, it's time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't, I won't...\NI can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!\NI'm just fine. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, the flower that\NAsuka Jr. was talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's probably called the snow drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only winter flower\Nthat has a delicious-sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Thanks, Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfume in Mr. Takarada's hand\Nis St. Tail's target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's keep the security tight.\N-Yes, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With this security alone, St. Tail\Nwill be associated with this perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if the notice is fake\Nand St. Tail doesn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Asuka Jr., this woman.\N-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko! I told you to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, please stop all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NThank you for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Invitation?\N-This can't be! The notice is a--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Something wrong with the notice?\N-Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the real St. Tail here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that sent\Nthe fake calling card out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Darn it!\N-Brother, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God sees through everything!\NOne! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm leaving with the perfume!\N-Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will let you get away with it?\NWait! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., the perfume!\NGet that perfume back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takarada, it's time\Nfor you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?\NThe temperature is-- It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it her famous illusion trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Father's flowers will die! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If the flowers die, we won't be able\Nto make the perfume! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, it's your fault. If Father's\Nflowers die, it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will be able\Nto make a wonderful perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...even without the use of my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget about it, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That calling card, I was the one\Nwho sent it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of completing the perfume,\Nall I thought of was how to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If St. Tail was after it, it would\Nbecome famous. That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., I should have gone\Nand told you of it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're white flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragrance of this flower,\Ncould it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The final ingredient in the notebook,\N"Earring of Snow," is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make it! Father's perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko, let's try\Nto complete it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, come down here\Nand challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You had me fooled all along,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it with words.\NI can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., I'm sorry\Nto have troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was stolen.\NSt. Tail has helped me to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:19:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This puts me on the spot.\NAll because of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.\NI can't afford to get caught yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get caught.
